description:
Naaman was miraculously healed by God, as he visited the prophet Elijah upon recommendation of a young slave girl, who is a key person in this story. While she remains nameless, her simple witness stands as an example to all of us today. No matter how bad our own circumstances are, we can still seek the best for others and point them to Jesus.
